Description:
Stunning One Bedroom Apartment in Docklands
This building is the next landmark building in the Victoria Harbour precinct and is the first residential building to have the prestigious Collins St address and also located on the Yarra. Perfectly synthesising our love of fast-paced city living with our need for rejuvenation and comfort, this is the perfect home and haven. Located at premium location, walking distance to tram, Sothern Cross Station, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco, shops and restaurants, great location gives you convenience and enjoyment.
This luxury one bedrooms at 15 floor offers a great lifestyle and comfortable living experience, features include:
-One bedrooms with floor to ceiling window, great view and plenty of sunshine
- Built in robes in bedroom
- Open plan living and dinning
- Full kitchen appliances (gas cook top)
- Air conditioning and heating
- Podium landscaped areas
- Indoor pool and GYM
- Blinds upgrade
- Fully reimbursed stamp duty
- Brand new
- Estimated completion in Apr 2017
Melbourne’s most iconic street meets the water. Don’t miss the opportunity to get a spot in this fantastic complex!

Description:
Price Reduced, Vendor Must Sell!
Don’t miss out on this huge outdoor living area at a reduced price! Striking with its stunning outdoor terrace that takes alfresco entertaining to a whole new level, this one of a kind one bedroom ground floor apartment in the sleek Serrata complex is something you’ll rarely find in the lively Docklands precinct. Private walk up access from Import Lane, combined with an open floorplan and contemporary class, make this a coveted offering. A bright and generous living zone opens out to the large terrace, while the excellent tiled kitchen has a stone benchtop and impressive s/steel appliances. A large bedroom featuring sliding door access from the living zone allows for flexibility when it comes to open or private living, while the elegant bathroom further boasts a concealed laundry. The apartment is also energy efficient and comes with secure intercom and heating. Enjoy cafes and restaurants right at your door, as well as Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, Victoria Harbour, trams, and Southern Cross Station nearby.

Description:
Essential Docklands Retreat in Masterful Arkley
A sensational opportunity for busy CBD professionals and owner-occupiers in search of a practical, contemporary, and relaxed Docklands offering, this one bedroom apartment covers all your bases in the exceptional Arkley residential complex.
The northern orientation allows for excellent views of mountain ranges and the Melbourne Star Observational Wheel, which can best be enjoyed from the sizeable undercover balcony and spacious lounge and dining zone with timber floors. The quality stone Stegbar kitchen is a functional space to prepare meals and also comes with stainless steel appliances, while the relaxed bedroom is equipped with a walk-in robe which is rare in a one bedroom apartment.
Other features include a renovated semi-ensuite with stylish glass splashback surrounds and European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a pool, spa, golf practice net and gym.
The Arkley is located in the brilliant NewQuay precinct with this area having access to superb eateries including Bopha Devi and Steakhouse 66. You also have dedicated trams taking you to West Preston, Bundoora RMIT, and the city, and you can walk to Harbour Town Shopping Centre and Costco.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Luxurious Fully Renovated With Stunning Water Views
With an air of elegance that will impress the most discerning of apartment hunters, this ultra-stylish and completely renovated spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the Conder complex is in a league of its own.
For those who want to relish the relaxed yet vibrant Docklands lifestyle while not compromising on quality, this completely renovated podium apartment is, just what you are looking for. Dark polished timber floors make a truly contemporary statement as do the stylish stone bench tops and funky designer lighting. A large lounge and dining zone will be a hub for everyday living, while the premium kitchen shows off with large island bench, oversized storage, stainless steel appliances including an induction cook top, and a Vintec wine fridge.
This apartment also boasts a sophisticated RTiPanel system that allows the owners to seamlessly control the property’s top of the line media and entertainment system. This system also allows the owners to remotely control two layers of electrically adjustable blinds and multiple T.V units throughout the property wirelessly with an iPad or any other smart device.
All bedrooms come with built-in robes including the master bedroom which offers a great sized ensuite. One of the other bedrooms also boasts a built-in desk suitable for a home office. The balcony looks directly out onto Victoria Harbour where you can almost touch the water and enjoy the sunsets. A tasteful family bathroom, separate laundry room, central heat/cool, 2 secure car spaces located on the same level for ultimate convenience, video intercom, storage cage are huge added benefits. The facilities incl. indoor pool, gym, and outdoor recreation area are other extras. The Conder complex comes from renowned architect Fender Katsalidis.
The NewQuay precinct is a wonderful combination of exciting attractions for both residents and tourists alike to truly lap up. The Waterside Oriental Bistro, Mint-o-Mustard, NewQuay International Buffet, and The Conder restaurant are just a few of the places to eat nearby, while Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco, Medibank Icehouse, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, and Festival Hall are other attractions. You also have access to multiple trams within the free tram zone right at your front door.

Description:
Pristine Package with Views of Melbourne Star
Whether you want to live in the vibrant NewQuay Precinct or take on a fantastic investment property which offers very appealing rental returns, this north-facing one bedroom apartment in the low-density Mariner residential complex is an ideal match for you.
This ‘Mariner’ apartment boasts gorgeous views of the iconic Melbourne Star Observation Wheel which is best enjoyed from the balcony with a wine as the sun is setting. Inside, love the impeccable modern touches throughout all living spaces, including the relaxed lounge and meals hub and black stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances.
Embrace one of the Dockland’s most popular pockets, where eateries such as Almina and The James Hotel are just moments away. You also have outstanding attractions moments away including Waterfront City, Costco supermarket, Medibank Icehouse, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, and trams which transport you to Wattle Park, Bundoora RMIT, and the CBD.
Other exciting features of this property include a bedroom with built-in robes, designer bathroom with laundry facilities, reverse cycle heating / cooling and intercom entry.

Description:
BRAND NEW APARTMENT WITH AMAZING VIEWS
Pagan Real Estate presents an amazing opportunity for investors or owner occupiers alike in this never-lived-in apartment in the chic M Docklands Complex. On offer is this beautifully contemporary apartment with remarkable styling, and amazing views
The open plan kitchen/dining area includes a stone bench-top island with breakfast bar, concealed dishwasher, Bosch oven and cooktop, concealed fridge, and plenty of clever storage solutions. The light-filled living room flows out onto the balcony with breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour to the west, and Mount Macedon to the north. Both bedrooms come with mirrored BIRs. The strikingly designed bathroom features timber finishes, black fixtures, and subway tiling in the shower, which includes a rain-shower head.
Rounding out this remarkable apartment is a Euro-laundry, secure swipe and video intercom entry, secure car space, and storage cage. Typical of modern apartment living residents enjoy the use of the complex's gym and heated outdoor swimming pool. In addition to these amenities, residents can take advantage of Peppers Privileges such as home delivery from the Momami Restaurant and vehicle detailing.
With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this inner city pad is perfectly situated on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD, and is only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
Stunning One Bedroom with Study!
Being situated on Collins Street but also directly on the Yarra River is quite unique, not just from a Victoria Harbour point of view but from a wider Melbourne point of view and it is that location that has inspired the design of this brilliant building.
The river-inspired design is the work of acclaimed Sydney-based architect Koichi Takada, making his first foray into the Melbourne market. His northern projects include Sydney by Crown, Skye by Crown and One Central Park.
This incredibly stylish building located at 889 Collins Street is due for completion in May 2017 and would make for a solid investment or the ideal inner-city home.
Spacious, light and bright, this large one bedroom apartment offers a dedicated study area, modern finishes throughout, amazing water views and a secure car space. Other features include:
·?Spacious 62 sqm apartment
·?Multi – function study area
·?Floor to ceiling window, great view and plenty of sunshine
· Timbered floorboards in Living, dining and kitchen area
·?Carpeted bedroom with built in robes
·?Open plan living and dinning
·?Full kitchen appliances (gas cook top)
·?Air conditioning and heating
·?Podium landscaped areas
·?Indoor pool and GYM
· Security entrance/ intercom
· Within Free Tram Zone
In addition to this, extensive communal facilities will be available to residents including private dining rooms, a games and billiard room, gym, pool, spa, yoga room and smaller “pocket” lounges for residents spread throughout the development.

Description:
3 Balconies, 2 Car Spaces, 1 Outstanding Living Experience
A complete triumph when it comes to utterly luxurious and stunningly spacious apartment living in the prestigious Yarra’s Edge residential complex, this amazing 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence has a 21st floor position as well as three separate balconies!
This impeccable property needs to be seen to be believed, with a considered floorplan allowing for both open and private living. You’ll spend hours lazing about in the relaxed central lounge and dining spaces, with this vast area adjoined by a stone kitchen with breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. This space also opens out to a balcony which takes in breathtaking views of the CBD and marina below.
The master bedroom is privately tucked away from the main living hub and comes with a dual vanity ensuite, BIRs, and a balcony, while a 2nd bedroom also has a balcony. The 3rd bedroom is situated right near the deluxe central and handy powder room which also has a European laundry.
On top of these main features, this apartment also comes with ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, 2 secure car spaces, over car storage and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. Don’t miss this amazing opportunity!
The Yarra’s Edge is a premium destination for those looking to make the Docklands switch. You’re located close to the amazing South Wharf which has a variety if sensational bars and restaurants as well as easy access to DFO shopping. This area is also near Crown Entertainment Complex, Southbank Promenade, and just over the Webb Bridge to the terrific Victoria Harbour precinct.

Description:
Ultra-Modern Lifestyle Haven for Astute Investor
Exceptionally located in the heart of Docklands, this immaculately presented apartment embodies a streamlined contemporary design with cleverly integrated living and dining areas set against a vibrant district outlook. It presents a readymade investment opportunity in this highly sought-after docklands complex, complete with expected rental yield of approx. $390 per week.
The generously scaled open plan layout combines casual living and dining areas, while a smart compact kitchen exudes style and is well equipped with stainless steel gas appliances. Additional highlights include a double sized bedroom with built-in wardrobe and quality carpet plus a modern bathroom, concealed laundry, ducted air conditioning, video intercom and lift access.
This impressive first home or investment is enviably placed within only moments from Melbournes CBD, while also just a stroll from popular boutiques, cafés, restaurants, parks and city bus or trams.

Description:
An Exceptional 27th Floor Yarra Point Haven
Unmistakable when it comes to its astonishing space, considered open plan design, elegant fittings and fixtures, and gorgeous Yarra River and city views, this three bedroom + study, two bathroom apartment in the Yarra Point building is the blueprint for sensational Docklands living.
Wake up and smile every morning when you set your eyes on the uninterrupted vistas that includes the river below and CBD skyline in the distance. These views are best enjoyed from the enormous main lounge and dining zone, and the spacious balcony which has a north-east orientation and is the ultimate spot for alfresco meals and drinks in spring and summer.
Miele appliances, and a large island bench are highlights of the light-filled kitchen which makes preparing lunches and dinners at home a true pleasure. Two bedrooms have great built-in robe storage with the amazing master retreat showing off with a WIR and a luxe double vanity ensuite. Further features include a main bathroom, study, separate laundry, heat/cool, video intercom, storage cage, and two car spaces.
Take advantage of RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna, while the location is second to none. The surrounding city, Port Melbourne, Southbank, and South Melbourne are easily accessible, while you can walk to South Wharf and enjoy terrific spots including West Village NYC, Meat Market, and Common Man. Also near DFO shops, Crown Casino, and Southern Cross Station.
